thread.title: Jo

author: Jo
title: Jo
text: I ordered online, so quick & easy the hardest thing I found was choosing a colour! My bike arrived from Melbourne to Qld in just 2 and a half working days, I was stoked, super efficient. My bike came with some assembly to do which was fine. It arrived in perfect condition. Fabulous bike great quality, I love it! Great work Reid Cycles, I've already started recommending you to friends!
